---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="OSHA Compliance — Recordable Injury & 300 Log Data">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-20 pb-12">
    <div class="md:grid md:grid-cols-2 md:gap-16 items-start">
      <div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-5">
          <span class="inline-block bg-[rgba(229,183,60,0.12)] text-[#E5B73C] font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">
            ⚡ Coming Soon
          </span>
          <span class="inline-block bg-[rgba(16,185,129,0.12)] text-[#10B981] font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-xs px-4 py-2 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider">
            June 2026 Tracking
          </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="font-['Manrope'] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight text-[#2D2D2D] mb-4">
          Thalux <span class="text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA Compliance</span><br />
          300 Log &amp; Injury Data
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[#333] text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">
          Aggregated OSHA 300 Log recordable injury data, severe injury reports (Form 301 equivalent), and employer summary data across NAICS codes. Every record includes injury type, body part affected, days away from work, and employer demographics — structured for EHS benchmarking, loss-run analysis, and risk modeling.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-[#666] leading-relaxed">
          Stop submitting FOIA requests and waiting weeks for inconsistent PDF dumps. This is the same data, pre-cleaned and classified, at a fraction of the compliance overhead.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-8 md:mt-0">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 mb-6">
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">850K+</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">Recordable Injuries</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">22</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">Data Columns</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">900+</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">NAICS Codes</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-5 text-center">
            <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-3xl text-[#E5B73C]">Annual</div>
            <div class="text-xs text-[#666] mt-1">Refresh Cadence</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-[#999] text-center">Data sourced from OSHA SOII and Severe Injury Reports. Enriched by Thalux AI.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Friction Teardown -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 border-t border-b border-[#DED8D0]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] text-center mb-10">The Compliance Data Gap</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-8 bg-white">
          <h3 class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3">🧩 The Old Way</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#666]">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Submit FOIA requests to OSHA for injury data</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Wait weeks for PDF dumps with inconsistent formatting</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Manually extract structured fields from scanned forms</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#DED8D0] shrink-0">•</span> Cross-reference across multiple state-plan agencies</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] shrink-0">→</span> Estimated: 40+ hrs / report in manual labor</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="border-2 border-[#E5B73C] rounded-xl p-8 bg-white shadow-sm">
          <h3 class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-3">⚡ OSHA Compliance Dataset</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[#666]">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> Pre-processed from OSHA public data portal and state feeds</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> Normalized schema with consistent injury classification</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> NAICS-level segmentation for industry benchmarking</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[#10B981] shrink-0">✓</span> Annual refresh with change tracking</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2 font-semibold text-[#2D2D2D]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] shrink-0">→</span> Your cost: one CSV download, zero compliance overhead</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Schema Table -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">Exact Schema (22 columns)</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] mb-8">Download the <a href="/data/osha-compliance/sample.csv" class="text-[#E5B73C] underline">free sample</a> to inspect before purchasing. Includes calculated TRIR, days away from work, and severe injury flags for every record.</p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-[#2D2D2D] text-white">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Column</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Description</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Example</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">incident_id</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Unique OSHA incident identifier</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">OSHA-2026-091234</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">report_type</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">300 Log, Severe Injury, Fatality</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">300 Log</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">establishment_name</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Employer/company name</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Acme Fabrication LLC</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">naics_code</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">6-digit NAICS industry code</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">332312</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">state</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Establishment state</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">TX</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">incident_date</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Date of injury/illness</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">2026-04-12</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">injury_type</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Fracture, Strain, Laceration, Burn, etc.</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Fracture</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">body_part</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Affected body part</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Left Hand / Wrist</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">days_away_from_work</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Total days away from work</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">14</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">days_job_restriction</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Days on job restriction</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">0</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">severity_code</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Severity classification</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">Moderate</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">employee_count</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Establishment employee count</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">47</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">trir_calc</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Calculated Total Recordable Incident Rate</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">2.1</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">severe_injury_flag</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Meets OSHA severe injury threshold</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">FALSE</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">fatality_flag</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Fatality indicator</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">FALSE</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">data_source</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">Source dataset (SOII, Severe Injury, etc.)</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">OSHA SOII</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="py-3 px-4 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm">extracted_at</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#333]">ISO 8601 extraction timestamp</td><td class="py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#666]">2026-06-30T03:00:00Z</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Data Preview Grid -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16 border-t border-b border-[#DED8D0]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">Sample Records</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] mb-8">5 of 850K+ records shown below. Full dataset extends orders of magnitude deeper.</p>
      <div class="overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-[#DED8D0] bg-white">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-[#2D2D2D] text-white">
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Incident ID</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">NAICS</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">State</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Date</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Injury Type</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Days Away</th>
              <th class="text-left py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">TRIR</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA-2026-091234</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">332312</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">TX</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-04-12</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Fracture</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">14</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">2.1</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA-2026-091235</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">236220</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">CA</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-05-28</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Strain</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">7</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">3.4</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA-2026-091236</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">561720</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">FL</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-03-15</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Laceration</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">3</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">1.8</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0] bg-[#FAFAF8]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA-2026-091237</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">622110</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">IL</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-06-02</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Needlestick</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">0</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">5.2</td></tr>
            <tr class="border-b border-[#DED8D0]"><td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA-2026-091238</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">493110</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">OH</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-01-20</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Burn</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">21</td><td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">6.7</td></tr>
            <!-- Blur overlay rows -->
            <tr class="relative" style="filter: blur(4px); -webkit-filter: blur(4px); user-select: none;">
              <td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA-2026-091239</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">238220</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">PA</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-02-08</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Amputation</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">42</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">9.1</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="relative" style="filter: blur(4px); -webkit-filter: blur(4px); user-select: none;">
              <td class="py-3 px-3 font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">OSHA-2026-091240</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">336111</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">MI</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">2026-05-30</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">Crushing</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#333]">28</td>
              <td class="py-3 px-3 text-sm text-[#E5B73C]">7.3</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
        <div class="text-center py-4 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#FAFAF8] to-white">
          <span class="text-[#999] text-sm">+ 850K additional records across 900+ NAICS codes</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-3xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] text-center mb-2">Launch Pricing</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] text-center max-w-lg mx-auto mb-10">Get notified when this dataset becomes available.</p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-[#E5B73C] transition-colors">
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">One-Time Snapshot</div>
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-4xl text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1">$49 <span class="text-base font-medium text-[#666]">USD</span></div>
          <div class="text-sm text-[#666] mb-6">One-time purchase</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Full dataset CSV</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Point-in-time snapshot</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Single commercial license</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Immediate digital delivery</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="w-full bg-[#E5B73C] text-white py-4 rounded-md font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-base text-center opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed">
            Coming Soon
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white border-2 border-[#E5B73C] rounded-xl p-8 shadow-sm">
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-lg text-[#2D2D2D] mb-2">Monthly Subscription</div>
          <div class="font-['Manrope'] font-extrabold text-4xl text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1">$99 <span class="text-base font-medium text-[#666]">USD</span></div>
          <div class="text-sm text-[#666] mb-6">per month</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8 text-sm">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Fresh data every 30 days</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Incremental change log</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Preferential email support</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2 text-[#333]"><span class="text-[#E5B73C] font-bold">✓</span> Cancel anytime — keep last snapshot</li>
          </ul>
          <div class="w-full bg-[#E5B73C] text-white py-4 rounded-md font-['Manrope'] font-bold text-base text-center opacity-60 cursor-not-allowed">
            Coming Soon
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Waitlist Form -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-[#FAFAF8] border-t border-b border-[#DED8D0]">
    <div class="max-w-lg mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="font-['Manrope'] text-2xl font-bold text-[#2D2D2D] text-center mb-2">Get Notified at Launch</h2>
      <p class="text-[#666] text-center text-sm mb-8">Be the first to know when OSHA Compliance data is ready for purchase.</p>
      <form name="osha-waitlist" method="POST" action="/data/govcon-intel/success" netlify class="space-y-4">
        <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="osha-waitlist" />
        <div>
          <label class="block font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1" for="email">Work Email *</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required
                 class="w-full border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-md py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] bg-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#E5B73C] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#E5B73C]"
                 placeholder="you@company.com" />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label class="block font-['Manrope'] font-semibold text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] mb-1" for="naics">NAICS Interest (optional)</label>
          <input type="text" id="naics" name="naics"
                 class="w-full border border-[#DED8D0] rounded-md py-3 px-4 text-sm text-[#2D2D2D] bg-white focus:outline-none focus:border-[#E5B73C] focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#E5B73C]"
                 placeholder="e.g. 332312, 236220" />
